snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls V: Skyrim Anniversary Edition and Upgrade Overview Video
snippet.description:
Skyrim celebrates its tenth anniversary this November! Take a closer look at the new content coming to the game soon, plus more on the Skyrim Anniversary Edition. From additional ways to play like Fishing (2021) and Survival Mode (2017) to questlines in Saints & Seducers (2019), there's something for every Dragonborn to get excited about.

Follow us on the following sites and social media: 
Official Site – https://elderscrolls.com 
Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/ElderScrolls
Twitter – https://twitter.com/elderscrolls
Instagram – https://www.instagram.com/elderscrolls/

ESRB RATING: Intense Violence, Blood and Gore, Sexual Themes, Language, Use of Alcohol
